name: Aegean
description: Native to the Greek islands known as the Cyclades in the Aegean Sea, these are natural cats, meaning they developed without humans getting involved in their breeding.

name: Bengal
description: The Bengal cat is highly active and highly intelligent. This makes them fun to live with, but they can sometimes be challenging.

name: Siamese
description: Siamese cats are known for their striking blue eyes and elegant bodies. They are social and talkative, forming strong bonds with their owners.

name: Maine Coon
description: Maine Coons are one of the largest domesticated cat breeds. They are known for their gentle nature and fluffy appearance.

name: Sphynx
description: The Sphynx is known for its hairlessness, though some have a fine down. They are friendly and inquisitive.

name: Ragdoll
description: Ragdolls are large, affectionate cats known for their calm demeanor and tendency to go limp when picked up.
